korean: 오늘은 할 일이 너무 많아서 정신이 없었다.
하나를 끝내면 또 다른 일이 생겨서 끝이 안 보였어.
이럴 때는 푹 쉬는 게 제일 필요한 것 같다.
english: I was so hectic today because I had too much to do.
When I finished one thing, another task came up and there was no end in sight.
My head hurt and my body felt heavy.
At times like this, I think a good rest is what I need most.
